name: services-core
include: .
depend: standard-library agdelte-store
-- The embedded store is the registered `agdelte-store` library. The agdelte
-- framework layer (FFI.Server/Json for the HTTP API) is on the include path via
-- `-i src` inside this monorepo. On extraction to its own repo, also add `agdelte`
-- to depend: above and register its .agda-lib.
